      "content": "Okay, the documentation and individual meetings make sense. I think I'll try that. One thing though, when I try to talk to them about it, they both act like they're doing nothing wrong and act really petty, like they're purposefully trying to annoy me and each other with small, sneaky comments. How do I handle that level of pettiness without losing my cool?",
